{"tid":803422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"厦門大學歷史系助理教授微博批「中國人低劣」遭解僱　校方：損害黨和國家形象","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T15:11:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"00528ae2d61bc9d683a3b84b01790446e56fac8f","tid":803422,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180902/s00004/f6221e29f99f1bb2dc9e66d0e4606ef3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2Ff6221e29f99f1bb2dc9e66d0e4606ef3.jpg&h=1eec33d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180902/s00004/f657f68ba77d0c0e5efa1f9e98462183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2Ff657f68ba77d0c0e5efa1f9e98462183.jpg&h=350d6302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廈門大學一名歷史系助理教授曾在微博發表多篇帖文，批評中國人及儒家思想低劣，校方昨（1日）召開會議處理事件，批評有關言論不符廈門大學教師身分，決定解僱涉事助理教授。<br />\n<br />\n校方指，廈門大學人文學院歷史系助理教授周運中，以網名「東海道子」在微博發表「錯誤言論」。就微博截圖所見，用戶「東海道子」在7月曾發文批評儒家思想缺乏契約精神，稱「中國人最高境界是說假話、做假帳、訂假合同」，是「最低劣的民族」。近日亦有發文指不會讓其子女外出吃飯，因「中國人最喜歡毒害同胞」；又曾轉發諷刺內地狗主無公德心的帖文，留言「中國人不配做人」。現時在微博已找不到用戶「東海道子」的發文。<br />\n<br />\n校方認爲周運中的言論歪曲歷史事實，損害黨和國家形象及傷害國人感情，逾越師德師風底線，決定將其解僱。有網民認爲涉事助理教授「被西方洗腦」、「是精日分子」，更質疑事主如何取得教席。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月，廈門大學一名女研究生田佳良亦曾在微博發文，以「支那」一詞批評上海迪士尼亂拋垃圾的遊客，遭紀律處分。校方昨日確認田佳良已辦理退學手續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180902/s00004/1535864617677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2F1535864617677&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=dc92660e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2F1535864617677&h=30ec9189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180902/s00004/1535864617677</a>"},{"pid":"880b0a3606a488c9bc2b2638d4cc8506fd4d9b7c","tid":803422,"uid":68085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae75c88d934188dc8ca30b8099efa7220f98828","tid":803422,"uid":190281,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真話姐"},{"pid":"f375634f3e7435db5ca875c8294912c21d38251e","tid":803422,"uid":143241,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"中國人不嬲都低質,從來都冇進步過."},{"pid":"c57085d846bb83ccd453bce2e5fe3efe699f4f4e","tid":803422,"uid":38177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"講真話ja"},{"pid":"231e31698a4da0431bacc8aabc88fc6058762374","tid":803422,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"全部都係真話"},{"pid":"fbfac1c03417fff8d3d09636c92b559a0fc377bf","tid":803422,"uid":81424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"乜原來仲有形象可以損害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388c3b49f3df2507f18afddf02ab46fbb32485bf","tid":803422,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"證實中國容不下講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c3cac8605ab9dfbbb5c7a17f6db357362489c4","tid":803422,"uid":46910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食埋最後晚餐好上路"},{"pid":"fcbfeea32cd5e1a61e03f2990e6d1a2e1551eeef","tid":803422,"uid":5289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"古時有指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n根本中國